                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{coursesUrl}}" class="cta-button">Explore Courses</a>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                New to online learning? Check out our <a href="{{helpUrl}}" class="support-link">Student Guide</a> for tips on getting the most from your courses.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Welcome to the future of learning! üéâ</p>
            <p>Need support? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="support-link">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 E-Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 